title: ⭐⭐⭐Everything You Need. All Right Here.⭐⭐⭐
posting_body: ['Sunchase Apartments is a welcoming, quiet apartment community conveniently located off of Highway 79 and close to IH-35.', 'We are just a moment’s drive away from shops, dining, entertainment, and schools.', 'Enjoy a day of shopping at the Round Rock Premium Outlet Mall or swing by Dell Diamond to catch a game or two.', 'Students will have easy access to surrounding Round Rock ISD schools as well as multiple college campuses.', 'Texas State University, Texas A&M Health Science Center, and Austin Community College R.R. are all less than five miles from property.', 'We are pet friendly and would love to have you and your furry critters.', 'We have NO breed or weight restrictions.', 'Sunchase Apartments is your one and only place for comfortable, easy living!', 'All we are missing is you!', 'App Fee: $50 (per adult)', 'QUALIFICATIONS:', '3x times the rent (before taxes)', 'Credit score of 650 or more', 'Background check', '(No felonies or more than 2 misdemeanors)', 'PETS:', 'NO WEIGHT OR BREED RESTRICTIONS', 'Pet deposit is $350 ($150 refundable)', '$30.00 pet rent', 'Monthly Fees:', 'Trash $10.48', 'Pest Control $4.57', 'Water $14-$16 per person', 'SUNCHASE APARTMENTS', 'CALL/ TEXT CHRISTA (not a locator) TODAY!!']
